headline: CBRE Names Co-CEOs for Investment Management Business
summary: DALLAS, December 05, 2024--CBRE Group, Inc. (NYSE:CBRE) today announced that Adam Gallistel and Andy Glanzman have been named Co-Chief Executive Officers of CBRE Investment Management.
